Lisa Alborghetti (amụrụ n'abali iri na itoolu nke onwa  June afo 1993) bụ onye Ịtali na-agba bọọlụ dịka onye boolu na-agba ọsọ n'etiti  na achi  isi na Inter Milan. Ọ bụ onye otu egwuri egwu nke otu mba Ịtaly.
Alborghetti malitere ịgbara otu ACF Brescia mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na ise, mgbe otu ahụ na-agba bọọlụ na ngalaba nke abụọ (Serie B) n'afọ 2008

Klọb ahụ ruru Serie A na nke mbụ ya n'afọ 2009 nke  Alborghetti gbaranyere goolu mbụ nke klọb ahụ na ngalaba kachasị elu. Site na utu aha abụọ nke Serie A, utu aha atọ nke Italian Women's Cup na utu aha atọ Italian Women't Super Cup, ihe fọrọ nke nta ka ọ bụrụ egwuregwu narị abụọ agbara na asọmpi niile n'ime afọ asatọ na klọb ahụ, a mara ọkwa n'abali iri na ato nke ọnwa June afo 2016 na ọ na-esonyere Apollon Limassol nke Saịprọs.
Ọ laghachiri Ịtali na ọnwa Febụwarị afọ 2017 wee gbaa bọọlụ nye  Atalanta Mozzanica Ọ nọrọ ebe ahụ otu oge ọzọ. N'afọ 2018 ọ gbaara bọọlụ nye otu ọhụrụ e guzobere A.C

Alborghetti nọchitere anya mba ya n'òtù ndị na-erubeghị afọ iri na asaa na ndị na-erubeghi afọ iri na itoolu, ebe o nyere  goolu abụọ na 2011 UEFA Women's Under-19 Championship megide Russia na Belgium.
O mere nke mbụ ya maka ndị otu mba n'abali asato nke onwa  Machị afọ 2013 megide New Zealand.
